	(text_box "NOTE TO BUILDERS:\n\nThis schematic maybe difficult to\nfollow if you are not experienced\nwith reading schematics. It contains\na lot of connections and can look\noverwhelming at first glance.\n\nFor a much easier step by step guide\nto building SPECTER, see WIRING.md\ninstead. WIRING.md lists every\nconnection in plain language with\nsafety notes and tips.\nThis schematic is here for those who\nwant a deeper technical understanding\nof the circuit, or who want to design\ntheir own PCB based on SPECTER. For\neveryone else, WIRING.md is probably\n10x easier to use and it is the\nrecommended starting point. :)\n\nCopyright (C) 2026 Phillip Rødseth\nSPDX-License-Identifier:\nCERN-OHL-W-2.0"
